Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還問我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明我怎麼央求 你都不許我進你的房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒問你 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 這樣說話很不禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀哎呀 這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們兩個還在慪氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不關你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭同學 我把維修人員叫來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也一起來房間看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 明明不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拍拍 拍拍 堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拍拍 拍…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 大家打開課本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天來講治療魔法中的精神回復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正如大家所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖魔法一般來說針對人體有淨化和防禦效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 下一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實對精神世界也有巨大的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這在古代的一次神聖魔法實驗中已被證實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅能夠治癒身體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還能排解低落心情 使之振作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}實際上將精靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通過說服精靈 借用他們的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 今天就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得好好複習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天放學後做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是之前去過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 看那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明不該變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在彈鋼琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手凍僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯！
